title: What are some off-meta picks you guys recommend?
body:
Been doing some off-meta stuff lately. I want some more to try since I've been having fun with it so far.

I've already done AP Nasus, AP Rengar, AD Tank Leblanc, ADC Thresh, and I'm going to try Lulu jungle soon. Wanted to do Cass supp, but don't own her sadly.
